  ## Introduction

  AMP HTML files don't support the normal HTML `img` tag. With [`amp-img`]({{g.doc('/content/amp-dev/documentation/components/reference/amp-img.md', locale=doc.locale).url.path}}) AMP provides a powerful replacement.
-->
